--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Talk_Stage11_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Localization::UnityEngine.Localization.Tables.StringTable
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4a5c93a12bc61c44cb71ddddf110527d, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 190110000000
    m_Localized: Thanks to you handling those sticky bombs,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000001
    m_Localized: we have fewer hazards around here. I appreciate it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000002
    m_Localized: Still, why are you so fixated on outside?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000003
    m_Localized: Because I know it exists?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000004
    m_Localized: I see.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000005
    m_Localized: Every time you talk about it, I feel drawn to that world too.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000006
    m_Localized: So I did some digging.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000007
    m_Localized: Apparently, one sector has a tall tower.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000008
    m_Localized: And reaching the top is considered the greatest taboo.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000009
    m_Localized: Why is that tower taboo?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000010
    m_Localized: Then, Yakumo, I hereby assign you to investigate it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000011
    m_Localized: Scientifically, I do not know.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000012
    m_Localized: People treat it like even saying its name is dangerous.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000013
    m_Localized: Then that is the place. Something has to be there.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000014
    m_Localized: Going there would be like trampling into sacred forbidden ground.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000015
    m_Localized: You are a scientist. You believe that kind of nonsense?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000016
    m_Localized: Whether it is nonsense or reality...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000017
    m_Localized: I honestly cannot tell anymore.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000018
    m_Localized: Hey, are you trying to get me locked up?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000019
    m_Localized: If no one finds out, fine. But if they do, I will have nowhere left
      to go.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000020
    m_Localized: Then become a wanderer.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000021
    m_Localized: You make it sound so easy.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000022
    m_Localized: Why are you telling me this?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000023
    m_Localized: Because I wanted to see the white fluff.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000024
    m_Localized: Huh?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000025
    m_Localized: But uncovering what lies beyond it...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000026
    m_Localized: might put a lot of people in danger.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000027
    m_Localized: And if there really is a god, we might anger it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000028
    m_Localized: I do not really get it, but I am going there. It feels like the
      place with answers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000029
    m_Localized: ...Right. Sure.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000030
    m_Localized: I cannot tell if you are brave or just stupid.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000031
    m_Localized: Better than standing still.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 190110000032
    m_Localized: That is true. Still dangerous, though.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
